      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable and honest ride? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to provide reliable transportation for its next owner! While it shows some visible signs of its time on the road, it remains a practical and functional choice for anyone seeking value and utility. Get ready to hit the road in a car that's experienced and still has plenty of life left!",
