    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find some minor signs of use like small stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is tidy and the upholstery is in great shape, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
