      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies reliability and sophisticated engineering. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a clean history and consistent service records, it offers a premium driving experience at an exceptional value. We invite discerning buyers to experience the performance and comfort of this distinguished automobile.",
      "price": 36500.0,
